History
*******

@{i}V 1.0@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} First release

        @{b}*@{ub} 4 boards implemented

@{i}V 1.1@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 18 boards implemented

@{i}V 1.2@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 27 boards implemented

@{i}V 1.3@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 28 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} Faster search algorithm

        @{b}*@{ub} Improved ListExp: shows board size and if board is shut down

@{i}V 1.4@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 47 boards implemented

@{i}V 1.5@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 76 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} ListExp: now it should work correctly if expname.library is
          not available

@{i}V 1.6@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 132 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} Added an algorithm that tries to find out the name of the
          expansion board if no product name is available.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added GCC inline include file.

        @{b}*@{ub} Revised the documentation

        @{b}*@{ub} Translated documentation into Texinfo.

        @{b}*@{ub} German version of the documentation is available

@{i}V 2.0@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 157 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} New function @{b}GetSysInfo()@{ub}: returns information strings 	about
          the system.

        @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}ListExp@{ub} improved to the new features

        @{b}*@{ub} GCC inline was faulty.

@{i}V 2.1@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 160 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} Bugfix: ShowConfig crashed after starting V2.0 of this library

        @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}GetSysInfo()@{ub} now returns information about memory size

        @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}boards.library@{ub} replacement written

@{i}V 2.2@{ui}
        @{b}*@{ub} 161 boards implemented

        @{b}*@{ub} Bugfix: expname crashed on unknown boards or manufacturers


@EndNode

